author: Og Mandino
message: I will love the light for it shows me the way, yet I will endure the darkness because it shows me the stars.
title: Thought of the day

author: Jane Addams
message: Our doubts are traitors and make us lose the good we often might win, by fearing to attempt.
title: Thought of the day

author: Thomas Carlyle
message: By nature man hates change; seldom will he quit his old home till it has actually fallen around his ears.
title: Thought of the day

author: M. Scott Peck
message: Until you value yourself, you won't value your time. Until you value your time, you won't do anything with it.
title: Thought of the day
